        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Before you spend more time on this, consider if this needs to be done in C. Do we already have the tools for users to put this information in the statusline themselves? Does `nvim_get_chan_info()` provide the relevant information? If so, users can just set `'stl'` to something that includes this without modifying the internal C code at all.",
